        "ggczQlFQuMx_text": "<p>☀️ More energy, focus with no jitters&nbsp;</p><p>🥥 Delicious coconut and vanilla flavours&nbsp;</p><p>🥛 Super easy to mix with milk, water etc&nbsp;</p><p>✨ Glowing skin, hair &amp; nails support</p>",
