        "ggybyXK4vI5_text": "<p>Free Shipping on Orders $50+</p>",
        "ggxrBsoh4hk_text": "<p>\"I’ve convinced all of my friends to switch from <strong>coffee to Teangle matcha collagen</strong>.”</p><p>Emily K. ✓ Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_0": "<p>Why You'll Love It</p>",
        "ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_1": "<p>Taste &amp; Feel</p>",
        "ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_2": "<p>How to Enjoy</p>",
        "ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_3": "<p>Is This For You?</p>",
        "ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_4": "<p>Ingredients &amp; Quality</p>",
        "ggfZlhvHMuV_text": "<p>Matcha Collagen+ is your new delicious ritual where matcha energy meets collagen beauty without the afternoon crash</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- Supports skin, hair, joints and nail health&nbsp;</p><p>- Helps increase energy, focus and clarity<br>- Two flavours: Original (Coconuty) and Vanilla<br>- Easy to mix, hot or cold, in drinks or food<br>- No added sugar, dairy, gluten, or weird stuff</p>",
        "ggYwsvXRD_l_text": "<p>Matcha Collagen+ comes in two delicious flavours:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Original: Smooth with a light coconutty finish<br>Vanilla: Subtle, creamy, and naturally sweet</p><p><br>And the feel? Calm and sustained energy, no jitters, no crash. Just focus, glow, and a little daily “ahhh.”</p>",
        "gg9FxdHduyz_text": "<p>Enjoy it your way - hot or iced, in the morning or as an afternoon boost.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Just add a scoop to water, milk, or your favourite alt-milk. It dissolves easily and tastes great every time.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Want to get creative?</p><p>You’ll get our free 101 Matcha Recipes book with your first order - packed with easy ideas like smoothies, snacks, baked treats, and more.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>There’s no wrong way to matcha.</p>",
        "ggQvk1UkYw3_text": "<p>If you're looking for a healthy daily ritual that actually makes you feel good - this is for you.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You want to replace coffee but still feel energized<br>You want healthier skin, hair, nails and a glow<br>You want collagen, but not in pill, capsule, or powder<br>You care about clean ingredients and no added sugars<br>You want something quick, easy, and actually delicious<br>Sounds like you? You’ll love Matcha Collagen.</p>",
        "ggUNyRmu8Q4_text": "<p>When it comes to ingredients, taste, and trust, Teangle stands out. We kept the good stuff (like organic matcha and marine collagen) and ditched the junk.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OG Flavor: 5g of pure marine collagen, 1g of organic ceremonial Matcha, organic coconut milk powder and organic acacia gum</p><p>ALLERGEN: FISH</p>"
      }
    },
